text: Margit Borg (born 15 June 1969) is a Swedish badminton player, born in Mariestad. She competed in women's singles and women's doubles at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Sweden Category:Badminton players at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Mariestad Municipality
